            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "# 📊 DBSQL Queue Breaker — are your SQL warehouses making users wait?\n",
                "This dashboard reads **your own** `system.query.history` and finds SQL warehouses where queries **queue at capacity** — i.e. the warehouse hit its max-cluster ceiling and made queries wait before they even started running. That's avoidable latency your users feel on every dashboard and query.\n",
                "**The fix is usually a ~2-minute, reversible change:** raise the warehouse's *max clusters* (autoscaling limit), or size it up. Page 2 lists exactly which warehouses and how many clusters to add. _Trailing 30 days. Read-only. No data leaves your workspace._"
              ]
            }
          },
